Dear Developers,

If you are on this pane, I suspect it is to ascertain the performance of my site. As such, I wanted to premptively explain the cookie warnings you will see in the console and `Issues` tab. These are erroneous, and generated by Google. Google Recaptcha generates non-essential third-party cookies, while Google Privacy Sandbox flags them. This is a known issue, that will hopefully be patched soon.

Additionally, for those generating lighthouse scores, the single missing performance point is caused by tailwind, and can not be avoided unfortunately.

